  "displayName": "Multi-Slot Input - Date and Party Size Together",
  "description": "User provides party size and date in a single message. Both setter tools fire, then batched readback confirmation, then FindAvailableTimes auto-executes. Name is deferred (BookReservation input) \u2014 no individual readback. After both name and requests are collected, a combined group readback fires.",
